WEBVTT
Kind: captions
Language: en

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:03.910
Now in this section, we will take a look at how to start several threads at once.

00:00:03.910 --> 00:00:07.380
To do this, you need to understand the fork-join parallelism,

00:00:07.379 --> 00:00:09.150
as well as the concept of threat barriers.

00:00:09.150 --> 00:00:11.580
Also you will learn how to properly store

00:00:11.580 --> 00:00:14.595
thread handles in a vector to manage them more easily.

00:00:14.595 --> 00:00:16.650
Last but definitely not least,

00:00:16.649 --> 00:00:19.099
you will meet your first official concurrency ban,

00:00:19.100 --> 00:00:21.395
k and I promise you, it will not be the last,

00:00:21.394 --> 00:00:25.120
either official or unofficial. Now let's take a look.

